.000Z","msg":"咁越南人危機意識一定最高喇<br />\n個作者咁奶台灣，真係唔知醜"},{"pid":"d20205ffe2cd47924b237033d9c0c07aea0e4aae","tid":2211163,"uid":52194,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T03:08:42.000Z","msg":"綠燈都可以右轉係好on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/nope.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcf8612abfb8e4665ec85561f634a2b5a974e61a","tid":2211163,"uid":196924,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T03:09:45.000Z","msg":"危條撚<br />\n一架二架綿羊唔睇人老奉咁過<br />\n人又係唔撚睇就過<br />\n日日都有人炒咁滯<br />\n台狗又打飛機"},{"pid":"c0b345fd3fdb7d55aac9467f4b4477b3ad874c47","tid":2211163,"uid":27568,"like":28,"dislike":3,"score":25,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T03:13:03.000Z","msg":"台灣係用日本果套<br />\n想行車暢順d<br />\n但要禮讓行人<br />\n點知台灣根本無讓到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港行英式<br />\n一刀切<br />\n費事你出事入佢數"},{"pid":"c96b42e0d5555f24899aa99b315b59b9cdf859de","tid":2211163,"uid":147367,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T03:15:56.000Z","msg":"從地理位置看中台差異<br />\n<br />\n台灣四面環海，沒有逃走路線，所以很有危機意識<br />\n香港只有三面環海，有安心的逃走路線，所以被馴化的很聽話<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n結論：去讀下邏輯先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd920cec44467da25aed4204828511d26622ac89","tid":2211163,"uid":65638,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T03:17:36.000Z","msg":"等我Sd 電郵屌柒條仆街"},{"pid":"d903e8c8d2a61abdea99da4938e3a78ead267742","tid":2211163,"uid":38757,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T03:20:03.000Z","msg":"其實...作者應該無返過大陸, 大陸咪仲勁?"},{"pid":"894c6b82125d6f618f4b4e3c088a67c758ce3d4b","tid":2211163,"uid":185184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T03:22:54.000Z","msg":"唔知香港定台灣嘅交通事故多啲呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07ea8bd090e54920c96ee91e40c7c38b08dee5d3","tid":2211163,"uid":47355,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"ci